title: Episode 46 - Japan - The Decline of the Imperial Empire
itunes:author: The History of the Cold War Podcast
itunes:summary: In this episode we examine the events leading up to the occupation of Japan. We review the forces which created Imperial Japan and the forces which led to its down fall in world war II.
